creator: InCust
descriptionHtml:
Coffeelat Loyalty Program
Provides you with the following options:
- checking the balance in the loyalty program
- receive special offers from Coffeelat
- authentication for payments at the checkout without the need to call a phone number
- private communication with the support service Coffeelat
- search for nearby Coffeelat sales points
- familiarization with news and special offers

With the Coffeelat application on your phone, you do not need to tell the phone number to the seller. Just run the application and show the one-time protected QR code shown on the phone screen to the seller. Get and use one-touch bonuses!
